   PACER Service Center

                             PACER Mailing List
   We are pleased to introduce a mailing list designed specifically for
   PACER users. Receive current PACER information as it becomes available
   directly to your email account. The information will include items such
   as :
     * Changes to the web site,
     * New courts on PACER-Net,
     * Quarterly announcements,
     * Availability of quarterly statements at this web site,
     * Availability of monthly transactions at this web site,
     * PACER Service Center closures for holidays or bad weather,
     * Solicitation for input from PACER users on proposed changes,
     * and more...

   To sign up for a free email subscription, log onto the account
   information section of this website, using your PACER login id and
   password, then select the 'Subscribe/Unsubscribe to PACER Mailing List'
   option.
